# Normalize text files to LF in the repository and on checkout.
# This prevents CRLF injection into Markdown/source files (see
# docs/BUG_ISSUE/doc-ux-readability-review-15fe4cbf.md, DOC-6A).
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicit binary declarations (safety net in addition to git's text=auto
# heuristic) for known non-text assets tracked in this repository.
*.png binary
*.zip binary
*.woff2 binary
*.bin binary
